videos.description: South Alabama QB Cole Garvin limps off the field with an apparent leg injury in the first quarter.
videos.headline: Garvin injured on keeper

videos.description: Mason Rudolph hits James Washington for the Cowboys first TD of the game.
videos.headline: Rudolph connects with Washington for 66-yard TD

videos.description: Mason Rudolph finds Marcell Ateman for the 4-yard touchdown pass.
videos.headline: Rudolph hits Ateman for TD

videos.description: With this completion, quarterback Mason Rudolph leapfrogs Brandon Weeden as Oklahoma State's all-time passing leader.
videos.headline: Rudolph becomes Oklahoma State's all-time leading passer

videos.description: Sophomore LB Calvin Bundage is ejected for targeting in the third quarter.
videos.headline: Bundage ejected for targeting

videos.description: Mason Rudolph finds Marcell Ateman for the duos second touchdown of the night.
videos.headline: Rudolph's 3rd TD pass extends Oklahoma State's lead

videos.description: Mason Rudolph rushes 10 yards for the touchdown. It's Rudolph's fourth total TD of the game.
videos.headline: Rudolph keeps it himself for the TD

videos.description: Justin Phillips intercepts the pass and takes it 25 yards for the touchdown in the third quarter.
videos.headline: Phillips' pick-six lengthens Oklahoma State's lead

videos.description: Oklahoma State head coach Mike Gundy praises Mason Rudolph as the quarterback sets the school's passing record.
videos.headline: Gundy speaks on Rudolph passing school record

videos.description: Dallas Davis hooks up with Maaseiah Francis for six to avoid being shutout in the 4th quarter.
videos.headline: Davis finds Francis to avoid shutout

videos.description: Oklahoma State QB Mason Rudolph discusses the Cowboys' 44-7 win over South Alabama.
videos.headline: Rudolph on Oklahoma State's win over South Alabama

videos.description: Adam Amin and Dusty Dvoracek breakdown Mason Rudolph's performance in the Cowboys's 44-7 win over South Alabama.
videos.headline: Rudolph, defense key in Oklahoma State's win

videos.description: Oklahoma State head coach Mike Gundy discusses how QB Mason Rudolph has embraced his leadership role on the team.
videos.headline: Gundy sheds light on Rudolph's leadership
